# Monthly Report Slideshow Project - Cursor Rules

## Project Context

This project is a professional slideshow presentation system for monthly work reports, built as a completely isolated sub-project in `v_repor_/`.

## Project Origins & Acknowledgments

This project was built based on the following sources:

